issue.title: Add song request page/resources
issue.body:
The existence of an active party corresponds to a currently running session that will hold the ephemeral queue.

The session manages the two-way communication between the control and the backend state. It also accepts song requests from the enqueue page.

The session must act as the manager for a phoenix channel as well.

issue.title: Create a Client Credentials service for Spotify
issue.body:
I'm lazy as hell so I'm going to do one of the following so that we can have some search going:

- Implement the API request calls myself in Elixir
- Defer to a small node server I start to grant myself the credentials

I'm a fan of the second one just because then I can use the node API with a baby express wrapper. But I'm also feeling saucy so let's try using now.sh ;)
